OL,3,CWorld's biggest jackpot game Powerball
OL,4,Cto launch in UK this week
OL,6,FThe UK version of the world's biggest
OL,7,Fjackpot game Powerball is set to
OL,8,Flaunch this week, operator Allwyn said.
OL,10,FThe National Lottery's Powerball will
OL,11,Fsee UK players pay #4 per line to
OL,12,Fcompete with their US counterparts to
OL,13,Fwin shared jackpots that can balloon
OL,14,Fto into the billions, which will be
OL,15,Fpaid out over 30 years.
OL,17,FAllwyn said players will be able to
OL,18,Fbuy into the game from Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
