OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784517497
OL,3,CWorld's biggest jackpot game Powerball
OL,4,Cto launch in UK this week
OL,6,FIf the Powerball jackpot ` which is
OL,7,Fcurrently estimated at 416 million US
OL,8,Fdollars (#311 million) ` continues to
OL,9,Froll until the UK launch, UK players
OL,10,Fwill be in with a chance to win it in
OL,11,Fthe opening draw on Thursday.
OL,13,FIt will be the first time the game has
OL,14,Foperated outside of the US and will
OL,15,Foffer UK players uncapped jackpots
OL,16,Fstarting at #12 million, which can
OL,17,Fgrow into the hundreds of millions and
OL,18,Feven billions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
