OL,3,CWorld's biggest jackpot game Powerball
OL,4,Cto launch in UK this week
OL,6,FThe UK game features an extra "match
OL,7,Ftwo main numbers" prize tier, which is
OL,8,Fonly available to UK players and
OL,9,Foffers a fixed prize of #8.
OL,11,FThe "match five main numbers" tier
OL,12,Falso offers a fixed prize of #1
OL,13,Fmillion while all other UK prize tiers
OL,14,Fwill vary depending on the balls drawn
OL,15,Fand the number of winners.
