OL,3,CWorld's biggest jackpot game Powerball
OL,4,Cto launch in UK this week
OL,6,FAllwyn chief executive Andria Vidler
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're excited to give National
OL,8,FLottery players the chance to dream
OL,9,Fbigger while supporting thousands of
OL,10,Fgood cause projects across the UK
OL,11,Fevery week.
OL,13,F"Powerball jackpots can soar into the
OL,14,Fbillions, offering breathtaking sums
OL,15,Fwith the potential to transform lives
OL,16,Fand communities.
OL,18,F"We're encouraging players to get
OL,19,Finvolved when tickets go on sale and
OL,20,Fwe'll be crossing our fingers for our
OL,21,Ffirst UK winner."
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@QO]
