OL,3,CWorld's biggest jackpot game Powerball
OL,4,Cto launch in UK this week
OL,6,FPowerball follows the National Lottery
OL,7,Fmaking the biggest overhaul to its
OL,8,Fdraw-based Lotto game since its launch
OL,9,Fin 1994, with players being given two
OL,10,Fchances to win for every #2 ticket.
OL,12,FThe change, which was rolled out from
OL,13,FJune 7, is expected to more than
OL,14,Fdouble the number of Lotto
OL,15,Fmillionaires ` from around 140 a year
OL,16,Fto about 345.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
