OL,3,CWorld's biggest jackpot game Powerball
OL,4,Cto launch in UK this week
OL,6,FIt also follows the recent completion
OL,7,Fof a #450 million major tech upgrade
OL,8,Fto the lottery, which involved moving
OL,9,F18 million player records and more
OL,10,Fthan three billion historical
OL,11,Ftransactions from old platforms to new
OL,12,Fones, and transforming the technology
OL,13,Fused by retail partners.
OL,15,FLatest figures from Allwyn show total
OL,16,FNational Lottery sales, including
OL,17,Flottery tickets bought in shops, came
OL,18,Fin at #8.1 billion in 2025, up 3.5% on
OL,19,Fthe previous year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
