OL,3,CWorld's biggest jackpot game Powerball
OL,4,Cto launch in UK this week
OL,6,FMore than #1.7 billion was generated
OL,7,Ffor good causes, which incorporates
OL,8,Ffunding for health, education, arts,
OL,9,Fsports heritage and charitable causes,
OL,10,Fand #967 million was raised in taxes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
